[
  {
    "startTime": 5.13,
    "endTime": 10.3,
    "text": "Friends, love ones, I've gathered you all here to tell you something important."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.301,
    "endTime": 12.329,
    "text": "You see I... I..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.33,
    "endTime": 15.5,
    "text": "Just spit it out!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.501,
    "endTime": 17.6,
    "text": "Yeah, Mickey. You're amongst friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.6,
    "endTime": 19.23,
    "text": "You can tell us anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.23,
    "endTime": 21.6,
    "text": "Yeah, Mick. Tell us!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.4,
    "endTime": 24.2,
    "text": "So, uh, you know how it's my birthday tomorrow?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.2,
    "endTime": 25.33,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.33,
    "endTime": 27.63,
    "text": "And you know how much I like my birthday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.63,
    "endTime": 28.799,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.8,
    "endTime": 32.13,
    "text": "Maybe we could skip the surprise party this year?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.131,
    "endTime": 33.2,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.2,
    "endTime": 34.6,
    "text": "Skip the surprise party."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.6,
    "endTime": 35.660000000000004,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.66,
    "endTime": 37.4,
    "text": "Can we please skip the surprise party?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.5,
    "endTime": 39.79,
    "text": "Gosh, Mick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.79,
    "endTime": 42.7,
    "text": "We thought you loved your surprise party."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.7,
    "endTime": 44.63,
    "text": "Uh... I wouldn't say love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.33,
    "endTime": 47.6,
    "text": "Surprise!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.8,
    "endTime": 50.66,
    "text": "You might say traumatized."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.86,
    "endTime": 53.0,
    "text": "Surprise!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.33,
    "endTime": 55.4,
    "text": "Or terrified."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.23,
    "endTime": 58.16,
    "text": "Surprise!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.16,
    "endTime": 59.23,
    "text": "Horrified."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.23,
    "endTime": 61.16,
    "text": "Surprise!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.16,
    "endTime": 62.16,
    "text": "Paralyzed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.6,
    "endTime": 67.3,
    "text": "But love, yeah, I think not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.3,
    "endTime": 70.63,
    "text": "I know my surprise party is your way of showing how much you care."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.63,
    "endTime": 72.5,
    "text": "But how about we do something small?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.5,
    "endTime": 75.3,
    "text": "Like, um...  A birthday cake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.3,
    "endTime": 77.16,
    "text": "That's a great idea!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.16,
    "endTime": 81.7,
    "text": "I believe the correct pronuncification is \"burfday.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.2,
    "endTime": 84.53,
    "text": "So, you guys promise?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.53,
    "endTime": 85.63,
    "text": "No surprises?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.63,
    "endTime": 87.16,
    "text": "You're the birthday boy. Absolutely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.16,
    "endTime": 90.7,
    "text": "Oh, boy! This is gonna be the best birthday ever!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.7,
    "endTime": 92.86,
    "text": "Burfday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.36,
    "endTime": 95.46,
    "text": "My birthday!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.46,
    "endTime": 97.229,
    "text": "No surprises."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.96,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "Who's ready to see Mickey's birthday cake?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.66,
    "endTime": 115.13,
    "text": "Oh, no. You call that a cake?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.13,
    "endTime": 118.229,
    "text": "This is no \"happy\" birthday cake!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.23,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "I need a cake that shows Mickey how much he means to us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 122.83,
    "text": "Something big!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.83,
    "endTime": 125.7,
    "text": "Not just big. Really, really big."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.7,
    "endTime": 127.8,
    "text": "Not just really, really big."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.8,
    "endTime": 130.53,
    "text": "Really, really, really big!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.53,
    "endTime": 132.5,
    "text": "Not just really, really, really big."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.5,
    "endTime": 133.86,
    "text": "Really, really, really..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.86,
    "endTime": 137.76000000000002,
    "text": "Really..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.76,
    "endTime": 138.959,
    "text": "Big."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.53,
    "endTime": 144.5,
    "text": "Oh, Donald. The surprise-free birthday boy is ready for his cake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.53,
    "endTime": 147.69,
    "text": "Donald?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.86,
    "endTime": 151.0,
    "text": "That's odd. The party was here last year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.001,
    "endTime": 152.0,
    "text": "Goofy's!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.3,
    "endTime": 155.86,
    "text": "Well, I figured the party would be down here 'cause... Guys?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.56,
    "endTime": 158.56,
    "text": "Minnie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.96,
    "endTime": 162.13,
    "text": "Where is everybody?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.3,
    "endTime": 180.16000000000003,
    "text": "Bigger!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.8,
    "endTime": 183.70000000000002,
    "text": "Yoo-hoo! Anyone?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.23,
    "endTime": 187.959,
    "text": "Golly, it's almost as if everybody's off planning my..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.3,
    "endTime": 191.5,
    "text": "Surprise party!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.46,
    "endTime": 196.459,
    "text": "We did it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.46,
    "endTime": 199.53,
    "text": "What's everyone standing around for?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.532,
    "endTime": 202.33,
    "text": "At this rate, we'll never make a cake big enough for Mickey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.33,
    "endTime": 204.13000000000002,
    "text": "Looks pretty big to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.13,
    "endTime": 206.299,
    "text": "Bigger! Bigger!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.3,
    "endTime": 207.66000000000003,
    "text": "You! Me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.66,
    "endTime": 209.329,
    "text": "Make cake bigger!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.8,
    "endTime": 211.70000000000002,
    "text": "Now see here. You can't simply..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.3,
    "endTime": 223.53,
    "text": "Bigger!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.66,
    "endTime": 226.56,
    "text": "Oh, they're out there somewhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.56,
    "endTime": 228.23,
    "text": "Waiting to surprise me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.23,
    "endTime": 230.1,
    "text": "Nowhere to run. Nowhere to hide."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.1,
    "endTime": 231.63,
    "text": "They could be here! They could be there!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.63,
    "endTime": 235.13,
    "text": "They could be... Everywhere!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.13,
    "endTime": 237.299,
    "text": "Just get it over with already!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.93,
    "endTime": 249.70000000000002,
    "text": "Traumatized, terrified,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.7,
    "endTime": 253.5,
    "text": "horrified, paralyzed!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.5,
    "endTime": 254.8,
    "text": "Help!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.8,
    "endTime": 255.93,
    "text": "Goofy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.93,
    "endTime": 258.0,
    "text": "Help! Goofy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.0,
    "endTime": 261.93,
    "text": "No more surprises! I can't take any more surprises!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.93,
    "endTime": 263.3,
    "text": "Hey, pal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.3,
    "endTime": 266.3,
    "text": "I know you're scared, and you just want to curl into a ball and hide,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.3,
    "endTime": 267.53000000000003,
    "text": "but your friends need your help."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.53,
    "endTime": 271.29999999999995,
    "text": "So, it's time to surprise yourself and go save your friends!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.3,
    "endTime": 273.39,
    "text": "You're right, I mean, I'm right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.39,
    "endTime": 275.2,
    "text": "I'm coming, Goofy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.2,
    "endTime": 276.7,
    "text": "Goofy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.7,
    "endTime": 280.26,
    "text": "Hey, Mick. You running from those giant, deadly candles, too?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.3,
    "endTime": 304.13,
    "text": "Quick, guys. We're going down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.13,
    "endTime": 306.3,
    "text": "We gotta lose some weight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.96,
    "endTime": 323.859,
    "text": "Bigger!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.86,
    "endTime": 324.86,
    "text": "Minnie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.33,
    "endTime": 326.659,
    "text": "Minnie!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.83,
    "endTime": 330.159,
    "text": "Hang in there, Minnie!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.7,
    "endTime": 342.5,
    "text": "Minnie. Oh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.5,
    "endTime": 344.66,
    "text": "I wish there was some way to get through to her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.36,
    "endTime": 347.13,
    "text": "Wish! That's it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.13,
    "endTime": 349.36,
    "text": "My birthday wish!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.7,
    "endTime": 365.93,
    "text": "Minnie, if you can hear me, I just want you to know it isn't the size of the cake that matters, but the size of the heart that bakes it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.3,
    "endTime": 368.40000000000003,
    "text": "The size of the heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 368.83,
    "endTime": 371.3,
    "text": "It isn't the size of the cake that matters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.3,
    "endTime": 373.159,
    "text": "It's the size of the heart that bakes it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.1,
    "endTime": 382.5,
    "text": "Minnie!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.96,
    "endTime": 384.96,
    "text": "I got you, Minnie! I got you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 388.93,
    "endTime": 391.1,
    "text": "Oh, Mickey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 399.13,
    "endTime": 400.46,
    "text": "Oh, Mickey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.46,
    "endTime": 404.359,
    "text": "I guess our cake turned out to be a big surprise after all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.36,
    "endTime": 406.33000000000004,
    "text": "Well, it sure was..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.13,
    "endTime": 409.53,
    "text": "Surprisingly delicious."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 412.1,
    "endTime": 414.70000000000005,
    "text": "Happy birthday, dear Mickey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414.7,
    "endTime": 418.86,
    "text": "Happy birthday to you."
  }
]